      <title>全球衰退贸易吞噬了华尔街的关税报复</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/global-recession-trade-engulfs-wall-street-on-tariff-retaliation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在金融市场的每个角落，从股票到债券再到商品，货币经理都向唐纳德·特朗普发送了同样的信息：他释放的贸易战争威胁要引发全球衰退＆Mdash＆Mdash;和快速。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/global-recession-trade-engulfs-wall-street-on-tariff-retaliation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 15:27:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耐克，lululemon soar so trump吹捧越南的富有成效的电话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/nike-lululemon-soar-as-trump-touts-productive-call-with-vietnam</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在越南拥有大型制造业务的公司的股票，包括耐克公司和Lululemon Athletica Inc.，在唐纳德·特朗普总统表示与该国领导人“非常有生产力的电话”之后，周五飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/nike-lululemon-soar-as-trump-touts-productive-call-with-vietnam</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 15:26:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔信号FED会对持续的通货膨胀冲击做出回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/powell-signals-fed-would-respond-to-persistent-inflation-shock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）表示，新关税的经济影响可能会大大比预期的要大得多，并且中央银行必须确保这不会导致通货膨胀越来越大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/powell-signals-fed-would-respond-to-persistent-inflation-shock</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 15:25:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>公共，私人市场的峰值关税不确定性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-04/peak-tariff-uncertainty-in-public-private-markets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在特朗普总统的关税公告之后，最大的私募股权公司的股票跌落。 Ares和KKR昨天都在记录中最多。摩根大通资产管理（JPMorgan Asset Management）全球私人市场和定制解决方案负责人杰德·拉斯科维茨（Jed Laskowitz）加入了彭博社开放兴趣，分享了他对市场对特朗普关税的反应以及他在红热私人信贷市场中看到的反应的看法。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-04/peak-tariff-uncertainty-in-public-private-markets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 15:24:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Newsom说，加利福尼亚寻求贸易盟友的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/newsom-says-california-ready-to-talk-with-trading-partners-m92wcdw0</link>
      <description><![CDATA[州长加文·纽瑟姆（Gavin Newsom）表示，他正在寻求对加利福尼亚制造产品的报复性关税的豁免，并希望与全球盟友就新的贸易关系进行谈判，这使该州成为反对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的大量关税计划的后果的缓冲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/newsom-says-california-ready-to-talk-with-trading-partners-m92wcdw0</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 14:45:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拉丁美洲资产领导EM RAT，关税下沉全球市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/emerging-currencies-gain-in-asia-as-tariff-woes-weigh-on-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[拉丁美洲周五领导了风险资产的溃败，自美国关税持续下降时，大流行和货币跌落以来，该地区的股票处于最糟糕的一天。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/emerging-currencies-gain-in-asia-as-tariff-woes-weigh-on-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 08:32:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当关税猛击金属和矿工时，铜的大部分时间都在5年内暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/copper-set-for-weekly-slide-as-tariffs-tarnish-metals-sentiment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[铜价在2020年3月以来的最大下降速度下降到每吨低于$ 9,000，因为担心贸易战争的影响会引起金属和采矿股票的大量抛售。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/copper-set-for-weekly-slide-as-tariffs-tarnish-metals-sentiment</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 03:16:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，越南愿意消除对美国商品的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/vietnam-asks-us-to-postpone-tariff-and-engage-in-negotiations-m923qrv7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统说，林的越南领导人愿意取消关税，以免惩罚对东南亚国家进口的新美国职责。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/vietnam-asks-us-to-postpone-tariff-and-engage-in-negotiations-m923qrv7</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 01:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔的关税重视之后，股票进一步加深：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股票的抛售加深，债券飙升和石油跌至四年低点，美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）表示，贸易战争的经济损失将比预期的要大，其潜在影响包括更高的价格和较慢的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 22:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
